      • addPublishedPapers

        public boolean addPublishedPapers()
        Adds the number of published papers to the Search Parameters if they are valid. If Start and End range are empty when the radio button for range is selected, throws error message. If Start is empty and End has a number entered, add the start range value to the Search Parameters. If End is empty and start has a number entered, add the end range value to the Search Parameters.
        Returns:
        a boolean flag
